                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9597" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">TM-0035</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">885 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">艺术赋能：夜郎谷文旅“合”能量释放之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Empowerment by Art: The Path of &quot;Integration&quot; Energy Release in Yelanggu Cultural Tourism</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吕宛青，肖钊富，何情税，宋志高，杨俊宜，毛晓漫</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贵州花溪夜郎谷喀斯特生态园</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">艺术赋能；文旅融合；文旅新场景；夜郎谷</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Empowerment by Art、Cultural and tourism integration、Travel and culture new scenarios、Yelanggu</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文旅融合发展是以习近平同志为核心的中共中央立足党和国家事业全局、把握文化和旅游发展规律作出的战略决策。夜郎谷景区通过艺术赋能，走出了一条文旅深度融合的发展路径，成为文旅融合典范景区。本案例剖析了景区发展历程，系统呈现了其以傩面图腾石柱群为核心载体，构建沉浸式文化体验场景、打造IP化旅游产品的创新实践。研究揭示了政府政策引导与企业市场化运营的协同机制，景区通过建立非遗工坊培育村民手工艺者形成的价值共创模式，以及喀斯特地貌与民族艺术融合的场景建构方法论。本案例深度阐释了利益相关者理论中“政府-企业-社区-游客”动态博弈的治理框架，拓展了场景理论在文化空间体验设计中的实践路径，验证了价值共创理论在文旅产业链延伸中的资源整合逻辑，有助于提升学员文旅项目利益相关者诉求分析与协同效应评估能力，培养对民族文化商业化路径的辩证思维，为乡村振兴背景下文旅融合实践提供决策分析框架。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The integrated development of culture and tourism is a strategic decision made by the Central Committee of the Communist Party of China with Comrade Xi Jinping as the core based on the overall situation of the cause of the Party and the country and grasping the law of cultural and tourism development. Through the empowerment of art, Yelanggu Scenic Area has embarked on a development path of deep integration of culture and tourism, and has become a model scenic spot for the integration of culture and tourism. This case analyzes the development process of the scenic spot, and systematically presents its innovative practice of building an immersive cultural experience scene and creating an IP-based tourism product with the totem stone pillars on the face as the core carrier. The study reveals the synergistic mechanism between government policy guidance and enterprise market-oriented operation, the value co-creation model formed by cultivating villager craftsmen through the establishment of intangible cultural heritage workshops, and the scene construction methodology of the integration of karst landform and national art. This case illustrates the governance framework of the dynamic game of &quot;government-enterprise-community-tourist&quot; in stakeholder theory, expands the practical path of scenario theory in cultural space experience design, and verifies the resource integration logic of value co-creation theory in the extension of cultural tourism industry chain, which is helpful to improve students&#39; ability to analyze stakeholder demands and evaluate synergies in cultural tourism projects, cultivate dialectical thinking on the commercialization path of national culture, and provide a decision-making analysis framework for the practice of cultural and tourism integration in the context of rural revitalization.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《旅游管理学》、《旅游规划与设计》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">利益相关者理论；场景理论；价值共创理论；文旅融合；文旅新场景</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-05</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
